{"title":"第四十个春天","authors":["乌吉斯古冷"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":7,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"第四十个春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌吉斯古冷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"延安飞来一片红云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给世界的红五月天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"添了一缕鲜艳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萨日娜花开了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年是第四十回。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"痛苦积久之后的喜泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从马头琴里奏出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂在花瓣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"内蒙古原来是一个美女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兴安岭是她的秀发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼伦湖是她的明眸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"内蒙古是富饶的地方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锡林郭勒草原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼伦贝尔草原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"畜群似滚动的麦浪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河套平川科尔沁平川"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦浪似滚动的畜群。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来白云鄂博是一座火山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思索了亿万斯年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才找到了喷发口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚下红河滚滚；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来准噶尔地藏亿万乌金"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"考虑了多少世纪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才捧献出来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑亮黑亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果不脱掉左和右的羁绊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骏马也会驻足不前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改革是一双翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"内蒙古腾飞了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们爱萨日娜花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而深情的歌是唱给太阳的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萨日娜花妍丽极了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全凭知时节的北京雨。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}